  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd  \u0baa\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bb9\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Don't act like Mr Bean - Vijitha Herat tells PM",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Vijitha Herath, a member of the People's Liberation Front, said to the Prime Minister that he should not act like Mr. Bean and tell the people how to solve the problems of the people as a responsible Prime Minister.",
        "Vijitha Herath MP during the Prime Minister's Question Time in Parliament on Wednesday (06). Point out the problems faced by the people and what is the solution taken by the government to solve these problems?. Similarly, the Ministers informed this House that the fuel ship will arrive on the 23rd.",
        "But now there is no hope regarding the arrival of that ship. He therefore asked what action the government would take against the ministers who had misled Parliament.",
        "The Prime Minister who got up to answer this, before giving the answer, just answer whether you are holding the government accountable or not. Your leader Anurakumara Dissanayake said that he will not take responsibility. You mentioned taking responsibility. Tell me something about it.",
        "Vijitha Herath M.P. Don't act like Mr. Bean and be a responsible Prime Minister and tell us what steps you have taken to solve people's problems. If you are going to act like Mr. Bean, come and sit in opposition. So you don't have to be Mr. Bean right now.",
        "You are currently the responsible Prime Minister of the country. So answer the problems related to the lives of the people we are asking and don't talk unnecessarily."
      ],
